01:12.672 --> 01:14.674
I'm late for a hair appointment.

01:14.674 --> 01:15.675
Oh.

01:15.675 --> 01:17.177
Hi, you two. Hello.

01:17.177 --> 01:18.178
Hi, Daph. Good to see you.

01:18.178 --> 01:19.179
Hello, Niles.

01:19.179 --> 01:20.180
Hey.

01:20.180 --> 01:22.182
Uh, my usual, please.

01:22.182 --> 01:24.184
Well, I've ruined another relationship.

01:24.184 --> 01:26.686
