01:29.189 --> 01:31.191
and, as usual, I made a mess of things.

01:31.191 --> 01:32.692
Did you say no?

01:32.692 --> 01:34.694
I said, "No, thank you. "

01:34.694 --> 01:37.185
But I wish to unburden myself.

01:37.497 --> 01:41.501
And I wish to remain in my good mood.

01:41.501 --> 01:42.502
