01:42.502 --> 01:43.491
You demur? I demur.

01:45.505 --> 01:47.507
Besides, I'm sure I've
heard it all before .

01:47.507 --> 01:49.202
But this time was
different-- I really thought

01:49.509 --> 01:51.500
BOTH: ...she could have been the one.

01:53.213 --> 01:55.215
Well.

01:55.215 --> 01:57.217
Silly me.

01:57.217 --> 01:59.519
To think that I could
count on my only brother

01:59.519 --> 02:01.521
for a shoulder on which to lean.

02:01.521 --> 02:03.223
What you need isn't a shoulder.

02:03.223 --> 02:04.224
It's a swift boot

02:04.224 --> 02:05.213
to break you out of this pattern.

02:06.526 --> 02:07.527
What pattern?

02:07.527 --> 02:09.229
Your pattern of ruining things

02:09.229 --> 02:10.229
before they've even begun.

02:10.229 --> 02:11.531
